4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior experience, aiming to equip them with necessary skills to become cybersecurity specialists and safeguard digital environments. The program spans 16 weeks, with three live online classes per week, accommodating up to 16 students per class. Participants will gain foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, and network administration, alongside practical skills in cloud security and penetration testing. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, acknowledged by various institutions. The curriculum is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop